{"tid":1720694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"扮藍絲文宣核彈！！藍絲實瘋傳鬧黑警(全城劇毒)","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T12:38:51.000Z","uid":336057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"14047f80439c10652b58bdd8de4af9863739ae29","tid":1720694,"uid":336057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇巴絲打諗過可以用藍絲廢老的心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n佢哋成班自私精最關心自己健康，藍絲最多係啲廢老同有細路嘅師奶阿毛。如果文宣重點寫大陸催淚彈幾毒，中左生畸胎生癌，加埋勁核突啲中毒相、畸胎相！而且毒物會殘留好多好多年不斷擴散，要講到放過催淚彈就住唔到人咁，觸發令佢地驚死心理狂share<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二個重點係，全世界得香港警渣先至會係民居度放，仲要香港人口咁密集，完全唔理人命！！！！等藍絲一見黑警就屌，你地話好唔好??????????????<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我是P牌也未整過文宣，文宣高手覺好可唔可以試下整？核彈啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022783a8ccc99cf51df2f8fc98a60caa7b03d959","tid":1720694,"uid":336057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541e97407d7953646b46a5c99b76594a416e17d2","tid":1720694,"uid":336057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi